LUPIN THE ⅢRD×MetaSamurai

This MetaSamurai is inspired by its movie's atmosphere and three main characters; Lupin, Jigen and Goemon. MetaSamurai is a 3D avatar project whose holders will receive membership access to exclusive drops, collaborations, and unique experiences.
